  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "High-Performance Connectivity",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "heading": "",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti Wave MLO5 (Wave-MLO5) is a next-generation wireless device engineered for high-speed connectivity over long distances. Operating in the 5 GHz frequency band, it enables a link range exceeding 100 kilometers, making it a reliable solution for point-to-point (PtP) and point-to-multipoint (PtMP) applications. This makes it ideal for rural broadband expansion, enterprise networks, and service providers looking to establish high-capacity wireless links. With a maximum throughput exceeding 5 Gbps, the Wave MLO5 ensures rapid and reliable data transmission, minimizing latency and packet loss. Its advanced Multi-Link Operation (MLO) technology allows multiple simultaneous connections, improving bandwidth efficiency and redundancy. Whether used in industrial deployments or commercial setups, this device delivers superior performance in demanding network environments."
    },
    {
      "heading": "",
      "text": "",
      "media": [
        {
          "url": "https://www.getic.com/images/catalogue/description/2544/picture1-67a1fe8e6da50-1100x408.jpg",
          "type": "image"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "Advanced Features",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "heading": "",
      "text": "The Wave MLO5 is equipped with advanced networking features, including dedicated spectral analysis radio, which provides real-time monitoring of signal interference and optimizes frequency selection for uninterrupted connectivity. The device supports Channel Puncturing technology, allowing for dynamic frequency adjustments that mitigate congestion and interference in crowded spectrum environments. Integrated Bluetooth functionality simplifies initial setup and configuration via mobile devices, streamlining deployment. Powering is handled through Passive PoE, supporting both 4-pair and 2-pair configurations with a voltage range of 44–54V DC. The included 10 GbE PoE adapter (54V DC, 0.56A) ensures hassle-free installation. With seamless UniFi integration, remote monitoring, and network management, the Wave MLO5 is an intelligent solution for high-speed wireless connectivity."
    },
    {
      "heading": "",
      "text": "",
      "media": [
        {
          "url": "https://www.getic.com/images/catalogue/description/2544/picture3-67a1fe950ebaa-1100x408.jpg",
          "type": "image"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "Powerful Hardware",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "heading": "",
      "text": "Built for high-performance networking, the Wave MLO5 features a quad-core IPQ5322 processor running at 1.5 GHz, complemented by 1 GB of DDR4 memory for efficient data handling and processing. The device includes a 10 Gigabit Ethernet RJ45 port and a 10G SFP+ port, providing flexible connectivity options for both wired and fiber networks. Additionally, two waterproof RP-SMA RF connectors and a GPS connector enhance the device’s functionality, allowing precise synchronization and extended range operation. With a maximum power consumption of just 20W, the Wave MLO5 is optimized for energy efficiency without compromising performance. These hardware capabilities make it an excellent choice for businesses, ISPs, and enterprises requiring ultra-fast wireless backhaul and broadband expansion."
    }
  ],
